
extends ../layout

block variables
  - var pageID = 'help-tips'
  - var pageTitle = 'Tips for Beginners'

block main
  article.ui-container-fluid.ui-mobile-expand
    include navigation
    .ui-grid-80.ui-offset-10.ui-mobile-expand
      section
        h4.ui-header-compact Tips for Beginners
        div.ui-skip-small
          ul
            li You are strongly recommended to read all the pages in our help center.
            li All the data you will post on our website should be restricted to 
              a(href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ASCII' rel='external' target='_blank') ASCII
              |  characters only.
            li Be serious about your actions: votings are irrevocable; reviews, comments, and messages cannot be deleted.
            li We use the ISO date in our database, which can be described as 
              code yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sssZ
              | . The timezone is always UTC.
